[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說除蓋障菩薩所問經卷第十",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "卿光梵大師賜紫沙門臣惟淨等奉　詔譯「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，能離八難。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a15_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、離不善業；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、如來所立禁戒而不違越；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、遠離慳悋；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、於先佛所植眾德本；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、勤修福行；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、智慧具足；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a18_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者善解方便；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、勝願具足；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、多起厭患。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a19_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、發勤精進。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩不造不善業故不墮地獄，設或示現生地獄中，亦不受彼地獄極苦，復不久處地獄之中，又不於彼有情生瞋惱心。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂以菩薩本性具修十善業故，以是因緣，菩薩不墮地獄。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a24_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩於如來禁戒不違越故，不墮畜生之趣，設或示現生彼趣中，而亦不受畜生之苦。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩不起慳悋，不以慳因緣故墮餓鬼趣，設或示現生彼趣中，而亦不受餓鬼之苦。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a28_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734a29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩不生邪見之家，設生於彼亦不壞淨信，而菩薩者，常得善知識共相會遇。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b01_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩久修善法，於先佛所植眾德本，而常於彼正見家生，於彼生已淨信具足，亦復廣大增長淨信。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩諸根亦不缺壞，若復諸根有所缺壞，即於佛法中不能堪任法器。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩廣集福德勤修福行，常尊重供養如來塔廟若法若僧，常所親近作諸勝行，由勝行廣修於己，乃得諸根圓具。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以圓具故，於佛法中即大法器。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b09_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩不生邊國，其中有情愚騃聾瘂，色力不具無所堪任，善言惡言不曉其義，於佛法中非其法器，不識父母、沙門、婆羅門。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故菩薩常生中國，其中有情根性明利，多有智者，復為智者所許，是所堪任具有力能，善言惡言悉曉其義，於佛法中是大法器，深信沙門、婆羅門。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先所修習智慧力故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b16_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩不生長壽天，若生其中，雖有無數諸佛出世，亦不值遇，利有情事不能成辦。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故菩薩生於欲界，此中有情值佛出世，愛樂親近而可化度。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩善具方便故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b20_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩不生無佛世界，若生其中，即不見佛、不聞法、不供僧，是故菩薩生於三寶具足佛剎之中。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由昔所修勝願具故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b23_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若聞諸可厭事，無有不生厭惡心者。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩纔聞是事，即起厭患之心，生厭患已發勤精進，修諸善法斷諸惡法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即能遠離八難。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得不忘失菩提心。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、遠離諂誑；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、正而無曲清淨潔白，遠離追求猶豫分別；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、受持佛法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、於法而不祕惜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c02_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、遠離法慳；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、不作障法因緣；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、無不實語；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、攝受大乘之法如說能行，於彼受持大乘人所起尊重心；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、於彼受持大乘人所，為漸入大乘故起親近想；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、深入大乘故，於說法人起師尊想。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得不忘失菩提心。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c08_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得宿命通。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、供養諸佛；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c09_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、攝持正法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、修持淨戒；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c10_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、除疑離障；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、多生歡喜；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、多作觀想；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、常住定心；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、生處清淨；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、常受化生；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、得明利識。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩由廣供養佛故，即能尊重正法，以重法故，乃於持法人所，以彼因緣能於正法受持讀誦，以所得法廣為他說，由是不惜身命，勤行修習受持正法，復能修持淨戒。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "戒有三種，謂身語心。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由其三業戒清淨故，即能除疑離諸障染。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c18_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先由戒行清淨，即能除疑離障；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "離疑障故多生歡喜，以心喜故多作觀想；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由觀想故常住定心，心住定故生處清淨；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "處清淨故常受化生，以化生故得明利識；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識明利故能知一生、二生、三、四、五生，若十、二十乃至百千無數生中宿命通事。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，得宿命通。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得不離善知識。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、不離見佛或聞或念；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、不離聞法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、不離供僧；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、不離於諸佛菩薩讚歎禮拜合掌恭敬或復頂禮；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c28_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、不離於多聞人所聽受說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0734c29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、不離聽受波羅蜜多法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、不離聽受菩提分法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、不離聽受三解脫法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、不離聽受四梵行法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、不離聽受一切智法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a03_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得不離善知識。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得遠離惡知識。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、遠離破戒人故，即能離惡知識；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a06_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、遠離壞正見人；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、遠離壞軌範人；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、遠離壞正命人；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、遠離耽湎之人；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、遠離懈怠之人；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、遠離沈沒生死之人；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、遠離背菩提人；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、遠離習近白衣之人；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者遠離諸煩惱故，能離惡知識。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩雖於如是等處皆悉遠離，而亦不於彼等人所生恚惡心、生惱害心、生輕慢心，菩薩但起是心：",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『如佛所說，一切有情諸界緣成，性欲相染習相近故即有所壞，是故我今離所習性。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即能遠離惡知識。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得如來法身。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、得平等身；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、得清淨身；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、得無盡身；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、得積集善身；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a19_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者得法身；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、得不可計度難測之身；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、得不思議身；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、得寂靜身；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、得等虛空身；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、得妙智身。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得如來法身。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a23_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等分位菩薩得如來法身？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a24_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初地菩薩得平等身。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而此菩薩能離一切險惡之身，遍知一切菩薩地法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二地菩薩得清淨身，善具淨戒故；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三地菩薩得無盡身，已離一切瞋恚故；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四地菩薩得積集善身，積集諸佛法故；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735a29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五地菩薩得法身，了知一切法故；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六地菩薩得不可計度難測之身，積集一切不可計度甚深法故；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b02_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七地菩薩得不思議身，積集善巧方便故；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b03_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八地菩薩得寂靜身，遠離一切戲論及離諸煩惱故；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九地菩薩得等虛空身，能現無量廣大身故；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十地菩薩得妙智身，積集一切所知法故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來法身與菩薩法身有別異不？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b07_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身無有別，其功德相而各有異。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b08_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何身無有別功德相異？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身實無異。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b10_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身者積集所成，同一相故，然功德相而各有異。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "功德相異者，其事云何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今說喻以明斯義。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b13_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如摩尼之寶，若不磨治與磨治者，二寶俱名摩尼之數。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而彼已磨治者摩尼之寶，光明煥耀瑩潔可愛，與不磨治不可倫比。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩身摩尼寶，如來身摩尼寶，亦復如是，如實皆同。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然菩薩身摩尼之寶，對如來身摩尼寶前，說其清淨光明之相不可倫比。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以如來身摩尼之寶廣大無量，滿有情界及虛空界，光明顯煥照耀而住。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來身摩尼寶者，磨治清淨離一切垢，不可以菩薩身摩尼之寶而為倫比。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩有餘垢故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如白分中初二夜月與彼望夕，圓明相遠體無殊異，法有差漸故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來之身、菩薩之身亦復如是，俱名為身。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然菩薩身光明照耀，對如來前不可倫比，其猶初二與十五月。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故當知，說如來身與菩薩身，雖同一相而功德異。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735b29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得金剛不壞身。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、不為貪瞋癡所壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、不為忿惱疲倦驕慢顛倒見等所壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、不為世間八法所壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、不為惡趣之苦所壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、不為一切苦所壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、不為生老死苦所壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、不為一切外道他論所壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、不為諸魔及魔眷屬所壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、不為聲聞緣覺所壞；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、不為一切欲境所壞。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得金剛不壞之身。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，為大導師。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、得他信許；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、為他所敬；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、善作指引；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c11_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、為他依止；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、能為濟命；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、善備資糧；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、富有財寶；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c12_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、無其止足；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、為作先導；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、善到一切智城。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何是得他信許，乃至善到一切智城？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師，若王若王臣皆悉信許，菩薩大導師亦復如是，若諸佛、若佛之聲聞弟子皆悉信許。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師，得婆羅門、剎帝利等一切人民恭敬供養，菩薩大導師亦復如是，得一切學無學眾，及餘天、龍、夜叉、乾闥婆等恭敬供養。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師能於曠野險難之中為作指引，令其安隱不生疲倦，菩薩大導師亦復如是，能於生死曠野險難之中，為諸有情指引其道，令知煩惱惡賊之處，使獲安隱不生疲倦。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師為諸孤露困苦之者作其依止，使令得出曠野險路，菩薩大導師亦復如是，能為諸外道等而作依止，使令得出生死曠野大險惡道。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0735c28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師能為王官及餘人眾設以所須作其濟命，菩薩大導師亦復如是，能為耽著生死諸有情類，設以方便作其濟命。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師隨諸方處若行若住，與諸商眾同涉曠野險惡道路期至城邑。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a03_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，導師善備資糧，令諸商眾同出曠野險惡之道，乃至安隱得到城邑。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩大導師亦復如是，隨欲往詣親近佛所，欲為攝受廣多有情，過大生死險惡道中，欲令有情悉到一切智大城之所，是故菩薩善備福智諸行資糧。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師欲止諸方富有財寶資生緣具，所謂金銀琉璃摩尼珊瑚車渠等寶，菩薩大導師亦復如是，欲止一切智大城故，廣集一切佛法勝行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師於其財寶希取無足，菩薩大導師亦復如是，於聖法財積集無足。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師與諸商眾善為先導。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a15_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為主宰故，善增益故，所作勝上故，能以愛語而攝受故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩大導師亦復如是，能為一切有情而作先導。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於功德法善增益故，分位勝上故，為勝主宰故，出實語故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如海導師具力能故得到城邑，菩薩大導師亦復如是，具勝力能得到一切智大城。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此等是為菩薩得他信許乃至善到一切智城。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，為大導師。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a23_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，善知正道。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、善知道路平坦；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、善知道路險惡；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、善知道路安隱；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、知其道善；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、善知道路流潤枯涸；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、善知道路處所；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、善知道路之相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、善知道路正直；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、善知道路詰曲；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、善知道路出要。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736a29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，善知正道。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b01_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，善能說示無顛倒道。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、應以大乘所度有情，即為宣說菩薩道法，不說聲聞道法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、應以聲聞乘所度有情，即為宣說聲聞道法，不說菩薩道法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、應以一切智道所度有情，即為宣說一切智法，不說緣覺道法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、應以緣覺乘法所度有情，即為宣說緣覺道法，不說一切智道；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、著於我執法執諸有情類，如應為說空無我法，不說我及有情、壽者、養育、補特伽羅道法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、依著二邊有情，即為宣說離二邊法，不說著二邊法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、散亂有情，即為宣說止觀道法，不說散亂之法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、愛著戲論有情，即為宣說真如道法，不說愚夫愛著戲論之法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、樂著生死有情，為說涅槃道法，不說生死之法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、住邪道有情，為說離其過失荊棘之法，不說煩惱荊棘之法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即能說示無顛倒道。",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說除蓋障菩薩所問經卷第十二",
        "from": "T14n0489_012:0736b19_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]